Package Entitites

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bottom
    Entity class for a Cupcake Bottom, built with info from Database
    Cupcake
    Entity class for a complete Cupcake, built with info from Database (a Topping and a Bottom Entity)
    Orderline
    Orderline Entity is created with a complete cupcake, an orderId(ShoppingCartId) and the quantity, this goes into a ShoppingCart class.
    ShoppingCart
    Entity class containing the complete order, composed of a list of Orderline objects, an OrderId, Purchase date and time and the username of the customer.
    Topping
    Entity class for a Cupcake Topping, built with info from Database
    User
    Entity class built form database with the information of the user that is logged into the web application.
